<HEADLINE>
THIS IS A TEST - THISIS A TEST 
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; PLEASE DISREGARD -TEST -TEST &QL;  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; WASHINGTON--This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
