   DELL _ As most of the personal computer industry has drifted
into trouble in recent quarters, Dell Computer Corp. has continued
to post higher sales and record stock prices. (Mahoney, Austin
American-Statesman) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
</P>
<P>
   BANKS _ The Texas Banking Commissioner is to submit a protest
against the merger of NationsBank and Bank America. Catherine
Ghiglieri, the commission, is to argue that the combined Texas
operations would surpass the 20 percent limit in deposits allowed
by law. (Golz, Austin American-Statesman) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
</P>
<P>
   EQUIFAX _ Equifax Inc. today announced record second quarter
results driven by continued double digit revenue growth, operating
leverage and strong performance across all four operating groups.
(Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
</P>
